<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2023-11-27T18:19:17-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2023-11-27T18:19:17-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-27T18:19:17-05:00</updated><title>随着平台规模缩小，Tumblr 取消了 Post Plus 订阅服务</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;粉色和紫色背景上的 Tumblr 徽标&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/CGicf72zLXXA-lYd6xYGgA-RYmw=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn. vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72907462/STK137_Tumblr_K_Radtke_01.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：边缘&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;lfpg1B&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot; https://staff.tumblr.com/post/735181452949536768/post-is-going-away-in-january-2024&quot;>;Tumblr 正在取消&lt;/a>; Post Plus，该功能可让创作者向用户收取订阅费用访问他们的内容。从 12 月 1 日开始，创作者将无法再在其博客上启用 Post Plus。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;csb4nJ&quot;>;Post Plus 的终止是在备忘录泄露几周后 &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/2023/11/9/23954412/tumblr-downscaling-employees-transferred-automattic&quot;>;透露了该平台在努力满足使用量和收入目标后的缩小规模计划&lt;/a>;。当时，Tumblr 母公司 Automattic 的首席执行官 Matt Mullenweg &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.tumblr.com/photomatt/733540451795206144/hey-genuine-question-although-im-not-honestly?source= share&quot;>;表示公司&lt;/a>;计划未来重点关注 Tumblr 的“核心功能”。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id= &quot;XtRp4x&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Tumblr 在未能‘扭转’网站后正在缩小规模”, &quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/9/23954412/tumblr-downscaling-employees-transferred-automattic&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;EKDKbv&quot;>;看来是 Post Plus，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2021/9/21/22684089/tumblr-post-plus-subscription-monetization-beta&quot;>;于 2021 年推出&lt;/a>;，是 Automattic 砧板上的第一个功能。在 Tumblr 上的一篇帖子中，该平台的工作人员表示，他们“最初引入 Post+ 是为了提升……&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/27/ 23978683/tumblr-post-plus-subscription-downsize&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/27/23978683/tumblr-post-plus-subscription-downsize" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/27/23978683/tumblr-post-plus-subscription-downsize</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-27T18:14:22-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-27T18:14:22-05:00</updated><title>网络星期一最佳优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;网络星期一用手机购物的人的明亮彩色矢量插图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/dsf1GiP4Phn-ykVroKnHQ8R1ieQ=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873 /cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72905335/236878_CYBER_WEEK_DEALS_AFernandez.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Aaron Fernandez 为 The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;hw6L8a&quot; >;长假周末后的星期一毫无乐趣，除非您想省钱。如果您错过了黑色星期五的所有超值优惠，那么“网络星期一”为您提供了在假期前节省大量现金的又一个机会。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;div id=&quot;idm7Ct&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;aside:11906226&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div >;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;bZLjoB&quot;>;例如，您仍然可以在购买许多受欢迎的礼物时获得大幅折扣，包括&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Bose-QuietComfort -Wireless-Cancelling-Headphones/dp/B0CCZ1L489?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Bose QuietComfort Ultra 耳机&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www. amazon.com/Introducing-sound-compact-speaker-Lavender/dp/B09ZXJDSL5/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Amazon 的 Echo Pop&lt;/a>; 到 &lt;a href =“https://www.anrdoezrs.net/links/8532386/type/dlg/sid/verge/https://www.sonos.com/en-us/shop/roam”rel =“赞助nofollow noopener”目标=&quot;_blank&q